channel.title: S0phont - Gliese (Xicon Remix) [Liquid Drum And Bass]
channel.description:
https://soundcloud.com/xiconic/s0phont-gliese-xicon-remix https://youtu.be/PuEA4kU_rRQ
Happy New Year, Auxy Disco! I am ending 2021 and starting 2022 off immediately with a new banger!
This is the Drum and Bass bootleg remix of s0phont’s “Gliese,” a popular song within the Auxy Community! I hope this kickstarts off your 2022 adventure as much as it did to me!
